data.description: A super cute updated home in the heart of town on a .57 acre lot. This home has a newer HVAC system, metal roof, new interior and exterior paint, flooring, and almost all the windows are brand new vinyl. The home boasts plenty of natural light, a large and spacious front room, and all the functionality one would need in a cozy home. Located minutes from I-84 access, the Oregon border, and so much more! There is plenty of storage in the detached shed for yard tools or toys. And don't forget the huge lot! You can build your dream shop if you'd like. This is a great home in a great location with plenty of options to make your own!
